__ Cantrip: Summon ___________________________ Cost: 15 ______________________

Use:  cantrip summon                           Material Component: none
Use:  C summon

The cantrip summon is a minor magic of the sphere of summoning.  When
cast, the cantrip immediately summons up a small creature of some sort.
While the creature will not be hostile, the caster does not have any
control over it.  Typical creatures summoned are mice, kittens, flies,
spiders, etc.
